OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FWords by Emily Youlton, Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FAndy Burnham became the UK's seventh
OL,10,Fprime minister in a decade on Monday
OL,11,Fafter ousting Sir Keir Starmer
OL,12,Ffollowing his landslide win of the
OL,13,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,15,FBurnham entered No 10 after a short
OL,16,Fvisit to the King on Monday morning
OL,17,Fand a no notes speech on the steps, in
OL,18,Fwhich he declared his primary
OL,19,Fdirective would be to end rough
OL,20,Fsleeping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
