PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FHe appointed his cabinet late on
OL,7,FMonday evening and then got straight
OL,8,Fto policy announcements.
OL,10,FThe former Manchester Mayor promised
OL,11,Fto lead a "cost-of-living government",
OL,12,Fand slashed VAT on electricity bills,
OL,13,Fbrought the bus fare cap back down to
OL,14,F#2, and launched his devolution
OL,15,Fpowerhouse, No 10 in the North.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
