OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FPrime ministers are at the height of
OL,7,Ftheir political power when they first
OL,8,Ftake over, and some polls already show
OL,9,FLabour's popularity is increasing
OL,10,Fagain as it seems Burnham has wasted
OL,11,Fno time cashing in on his political
OL,12,Fcapital.
OL,14,FITV News breaks down Burnham's first
OL,15,Fweek policies and his plans to deliver
OL,16,Fthem.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
