OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FLate on Monday evening, the
OL,7,Fannouncements of Burnham's cabinet
OL,8,Ftrickled through, with John Healey
OL,9,Fbecoming chancellor in an unexpected
OL,10,Fmove.
OL,12,FThe former defence secretary resigned
OL,13,Ffrom Starmer's government over a row
OL,14,Fon defence investment, claiming that
OL,15,Fthe deal that the former PM was not
OL,16,Fenough funds to keep the country safe.
OL,18,FNow he will be the one to decide how
OL,19,Fmuch money should be spent on defence
OL,20,F- and which other department might
OL,21,Flose out to pay for it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
