FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FBoth Healey and Burnham have promised
OL,7,Fto stick to the fiscal rules set out
OL,8,Fby former chancellor Rachel Reeves,
OL,9,Fwhich include not borrowing for day-to-
OL,10,Fday government operations.
OL,12,FBut it remains to be seen whether they
OL,13,Fwill be able to commit to this long
OL,14,Fterm and deliver all of their new
OL,15,Fpolicies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
