OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FBucking the Labour tradition, Burnham
OL,7,Fdidn't select a deputy but instead
OL,8,Fbestowed the title of First Secretary
OL,9,Fof State upon his right hand woman,
OL,10,FLouise Haigh, which is the equivalent
OL,11,Frole in all but name.
OL,13,FThe former transport secretary was
OL,14,Fforced to resign from Starmer's
OL,15,Fgovernment after she pled guilty to
OL,16,Ffalsely reporting a stolen phone to
OL,17,Fthe police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
