OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FAnother figure who was forced to
OL,7,Fresign from Starmer's top team over a
OL,8,Fscandal was Angela Rayner, who has re-
OL,9,Fentered the cabinet as housing
OL,10,Fsecretary after she was cleared of any
OL,11,Fwrongdoing in relation to tax paid on
OL,12,Fher property.
OL,14,FRayner, who grew up in social housing,
OL,15,Fwill now lead Burnham's potential plan
OL,16,Ffor the "biggest council housebuilding
OL,17,Fprogramme since the post-war period".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
