OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar got
OL,7,Fa new job too, heading into the Lords
OL,8,Fand becoming a minister in the new
OL,9,Fbeefed up Department for Business,
OL,10,FInnovation, Science and Trade.
OL,12,FSarwar was the first senior Labour
OL,13,Ffigure to call for Starmer to resign,
OL,14,Fso it could be seen that this new
OL,15,Fgovernment position is a reward for
OL,16,Fthe role he played in Burnham
OL,17,Feventually becoming PM.
OL,19,FCost-of-living
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
