OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FOn day two, Burnham convened his top
OL,7,Fteam and told them they were going to
OL,8,Fbe a "cost-of-living government" as he
OL,9,Fstarted rolling out his policies.
OL,11,FThe first one was a cut to the VAT on
OL,12,Felectricity bills in England, Scotland
OL,13,Fand Wales from 5% to 0% from October
OL,14,F1, lasting six months.
OL,16,FIt's estimated to save the average
OL,17,Fhousehold #45 over that period, but
OL,18,Fwith the energy price cap set to rise
OL,19,Fby more than 3% at the same time, the
OL,20,Freal time saving may be closer to #20.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
