PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FFormer cabinet member Darren Jones,
OL,7,Fquestion the funding of the plan,
OL,8,Fwhich team Burnham said would be from
OL,9,Fthe cancellation of Starmer's Digital
OL,10,FID scheme.
OL,12,FThis led Starmer ally Jones to take to
OL,13,Fsocial media to claim that the ID
OL,14,Fproject was "unfunded".
OL,16,FWednesday brought another policy to
OL,17,Fhelp the public save some money as the
OL,18,FKing of the North finally made a visit
OL,19,Fto the south-west of England, heading
OL,20,Fto Bath to announce the return of the
OL,21,F#2 bus fare cap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
