OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FThis will apply to single journeys in
OL,7,FEngland, outside of London, where a
OL,8,Ffare is even less at #1.75, and
OL,9,FManchester, which already had the cap
OL,10,Fin place from Burnham's days as mayor.
OL,12,FThe cap was raised in January last
OL,13,Fyear by Starmer's government to #3,
OL,14,Fbut the new PM has reversed this to
OL,15,F"put money in people's pockets".
OL,17,FThe saving will start in March 2027
OL,18,Fand continue for at least a year and
OL,19,Fwill cost more than #500 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
