OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FIt will be funded by switching
OL,7,Finternational climate finance grants
OL,8,Fto loans, with the rest from savings
OL,9,Fin the Department for Energy Security
OL,10,Fand Net Zero budget.
OL,12,FThe Department for Transport will top
OL,13,Fup the budget with the cash already
OL,14,Fallocated to buses and there's money
OL,15,Fto allow devolved governments to take
OL,16,Fsimilar action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
