OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FThere were other ideas floating around
OL,7,Ffor cost-of-living action, with
OL,8,FBurnham repeatedly mentioning the
OL,9,Fpersonal tax threshold, saying it was
OL,10,Fan issue raised on doorsteps while he
OL,11,Fwas campaigning in Makerfield.
OL,13,FThe tax-free threshold currently sits
OL,14,Fat #12,570 and has been frozen at that
OL,15,Frate since April 2021, but Burnham has
OL,16,Fnow ruled out any immediate changes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
