OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FHe said: "It was raised a lot, but I
OL,7,Fthen went on to say, 'But we'll have
OL,8,Fto look at it at the budget alongside
OL,9,Feverything else'. So no commitment, no
OL,10,Funfunded promise."
OL,12,FOn Friday morning, the housing
OL,13,Fsecretary also ruled out a potential
OL,14,Fpolicy of rent freezes.
OL,16,FFor a prime minister who claimed he'd
OL,17,Frather "a beer and chips and gravy any
OL,18,Fday" over a biscuit, it's might not be
OL,19,Fa surprise he launched a policy to cut
OL,20,Fbusiness rates on pubs.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
