OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the PM and Healey pledged
OL,7,Fa 20% cut for pubs, clubs and music
OL,8,Fvenues, estimated to help nearly
OL,9,F32,000 venues across England, and
OL,10,Fgenerate an annual saving of #1,100
OL,11,Ffor a pub.
OL,13,FBurnham said "pubs need to know the
OL,14,Fcavalry is coming" as he hoped the cut
OL,15,Fwould save "our heritage" and "working
OL,16,Fclass culture".
OL,18,FThe cut will be funded by increases on
OL,19,Ftax for business like vape shops,
OL,20,Fwhich cause "social harm" and will
OL,21,Fcome in to effect from next April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
