OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FOn Friday, Rayner acknowledged this
OL,7,Fwasn't going to fix everything for
OL,8,Fhospitality businesses and the high
OL,9,Fstreet, with restaurant and cafe
OL,10,Fowners criticising their exclusion.
OL,12,FShe said: "The prime minister wants to
OL,13,Fbear down on those costs and in his
OL,14,Ffirst week he's set out some changes,
OL,15,FI accept it isn't everything that the
OL,16,Fsector wants but it's an intention to
OL,17,Fshow that we get it and we want to do
OL,18,Fsomething about this."
OL,20,FNo 10 North
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
