OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FA day after pints in Harlow, Burnham
OL,7,Freturned to his beloved Manchester to
OL,8,Flaunch No 10 North, a project he
OL,9,Fpledged in the run up to being crowned
OL,10,FLabour leader.
OL,12,FThe aim of this north west bureau is
OL,13,Fto "drive devolution" and deliver
OL,14,F"good growth in every post code" with
OL,15,Fother cabinet ministers including
OL,16,FRayner, new education secretary Lucy
OL,17,FPowell and First Secretary of State
OL,18,FHaigh expected to work there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
