CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784913524
OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FThe prime minister hopes to work from
OL,7,Fthere at least once a week, insisting
OL,8,Fit isn't a "gimmick" but instead a
OL,9,Fmove of power away from Whitehall.
OL,11,FThere are already civil service
OL,12,Fdepartments in Manchester, with the
OL,13,Fnew No 10 sharing it's home with GCHQ
OL,14,Fand the Treasury having a base in
OL,15,FDarlington, but there are set to be
OL,16,Faround 300 civil servants now based at
OL,17,Fthe PM's new second home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
