OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FAgain, questions have been raised
OL,7,Fabout what this might cost, but on
OL,8,FFriday Rayner was quick to confirm any
OL,9,Fspend was from existing cabinet office
OL,10,Fbudgets "so it won't cost taxpayers
OL,11,Fany more money".
OL,13,FDuring it's launch day, Burnham
OL,14,Fconvened the National Economic Council
OL,15,F(NEC), first launched in 2008 under
OL,16,FGordon Brown to deal with the economic
OL,17,Fcrisis, to coordinate businesses and
OL,18,Fthe delivery of his devolution plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
