OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FHe's faced criticism that his
OL,7,Fdevolution plans are only focusing on
OL,8,FManchester and the North but in his
OL,9,Flaunch speech, he was keen to explain
OL,10,Fthis wasn't the case.
OL,12,FBurnham said: "This is the place where
OL,13,FWhitehall meets the rest of the
OL,14,Fcountry. I've called it the nerve
OL,15,Fcentre for a rewired Britain."
OL,17,FHe also said it was the "North Pole
OL,18,Fthat balances the South Pole", and
OL,19,Fquestions still remain on how a
OL,20,FManchester base will benefit the other
OL,21,Fends of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
