OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FThings Burnham can't plan for
OL,8,FA prime minister's workload can't
OL,9,Falways be predicted, and with conflict
OL,10,Fstill ongoing in the Middle East,
OL,11,FBurnham's had to confirm the US can
OL,12,Fcontinue to use UK bases.
OL,14,FThe government confirmed the UK
OL,15,F"stands ready 24/7 to defend itself"
OL,16,Fafter Iran accused them of
OL,17,F"complicity" with the US acts in the
OL,18,Fregion.
