OL,3,CHow has Andy Burnham's first week as
OL,4,Cprime minister unfolded?
OL,6,FWhile the government has refused to
OL,7,Ftake part in offensive campaigns
OL,8,Fagainst Iran, it has allowed the US to
OL,9,Flaunch defensive strikes from British
OL,10,Fbases hosting American personnel.
OL,12,FBurnham also "put a pause" on the
OL,13,Fearly release scheme introduced to
OL,14,Fmanage prison capacity following
OL,15,Foutcry from the family of PC Harper,
OL,16,Fwho's killers could have been released
OL,17,Fas part of the plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/23
